Entries.default: "Hm, quaint place. The Republics sure know how to gussy up a village."
"By Ngati, you would not guess that these were once Huana lands."
"I've missed this place. Though not Thorel's porridge."
"Do I hear a tavern? We picked the right island to get marooned on."
"Port Maje is a quaint little town, but not a bad place to spend some time."
"Seem to remember picking you up round bout here. Forget something, did you?"
"Ah, we're back! Wonder if Waenglith's still in a mood."
"I sailed through here on my way to Neketaka. Saw the dig site. The man in charge of the excavation was... quite set in his theories."
